  "description": "A stunning nighttime view of a city skyline, prominently featuring two bridges and a vibrant fireworks display. The foreground showcases a modern, illuminated bridge with sleek lines and white lights stretching across dark water. Behind it, the iconic, red suspension bridge is visible, also illuminated. The city skyline rises majestically in the background, a tapestry of illuminated buildings and skyscrapers. Above the cityscape, a spectacular burst of fireworks illuminates the night sky with shades of red, white, and blue, forming a complex floral pattern. The overall scene evokes a sense of celebration and urban grandeur.",
